ion step plus downstream checks and approval gating. This is a full agent pipeline, so minimum level is Workflow. Rejected lower levels because they cannot validate cross-stage ordering/state propagation through the complete sequence described.","test_description":"Run an end-to-end scenario on a real email thread: ingest thread, generate draft with real LLM, run fact-check stage, present approval UI/state, and confirm send is blocked until approval; assert artifacts and state transitions at each stage.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.01,"Integration":0.09,"System":0.18,"Agentic":0.12,"Workflow":0.6}}]}
